de.mpa.client.model.dbsearch

Class DbSearchResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mpa.client.model.dbsearch.DbSearchResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class DbSearchResult
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class represents the set of proteins which may hold multiple peptides for each protein hit (identified by its accession number).
    Author:
    T. Muth, R. Heyer
